### ============================================================
### 활동 피드 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 전체 공개 피드 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/public?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 카테고리별 공개 피드 조회 (categoryId 사용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/public?page=0&size=20&categoryId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 타임라인 피드 조회 (내 + 친구 피드)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/timeline?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 특정 사용자의 피드 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/user/target-user-id?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 피드 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/guild/1?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 카테고리별 피드 조회
### Category: MISSION_COMPLETE, ACHIEVEMENT, GUILD_JOIN, etc.
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/category/MISSION_COMPLETE?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 피드 검색 (전체 카테고리)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/search?keyword=morning&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 피드 검색 (특정 카테고리 내)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/search?keyword=morning&category=MISSION_COMPLETE&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 피드 상세 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 피드 생성 (사용자 직접 생성)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "content": "Today I completed my first mission!",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 피드 삭제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 좋아요 토글
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 댓글 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/1/comments?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: ko

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 댓글 작성
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/1/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "content": "Great job! Keep it up!"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 댓글 삭제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feeds/1/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
